{"product_id":"madara-the-eye-pencil-black","title":"MÁDARA The Eye Pencil Black 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFormulated with rich mineral pigments, this natural certified eye pencil delivers vibrant colour and a smooth application to help you create any eye makeup look you desire. Its long-lasting, creamy formula glides onto the skin effortlessly without tugging or pulling, making it ideal for creating smudged smoky eyes or defining the eye shape. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Eye Pencil features a wooden barrel and a recyclable plastic cap while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply it directly to the waterline for a more dramatic look. To open and elongate the eyes, draw it close to the lash line. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); C10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; MICA (CI 77019); TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e16% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52308696105287,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-the-eye-pencil-black-1g-5135248.jpg?v=1762389188","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-the-eye-pencil-black","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}